  "texts": [
    "The input layer was 7-mer amino acid sequences one-hot encoded into a 20 × 7 matrix.",
    "The target/output is the relative production or functional fitness score.",
    "The loss was optimized by mean-squared error with the Adam optimizer running on a learning rate of 0.001 28.",
    "The batch size was set to 500 observations.",
    "To avoid overfitting, model training was controlled by a custom early stopping procedure where the training process was terminated if the ratio of training error to validation error dropped below 0.90."
